      • setPlacement

        public VMTypes.InstantCloneSpec.Builder setPlacement(VMTypes.InstantClonePlacementSpec placement)
        Virtual machine placement information. This property was added in vSphere API 6.7.1. If this property is null, the system will use the values from the source virtual machine. If specified, each field will be used for placement. If the fields result in disjoint placement the operation will fail. If the fields along with the placement values of the source virtual machine result in disjoint placement the operation will fail.
        Parameters:
        placement - New value for the property.
